flowRoot.flowPara: I tweaked from this point to support Tslots for the 'top'.
When using TSlots the bolt diameter is #4 and length is 0.5".
Metric close equivalents are an M3 with 12mm length.
The Kerf setting (which is shown as "Kerf (Beam Diameter /2 )") is 0.005"
(I tried 0.007" but it was a little bit too tight.)
